  "questions": [
    {
      "text": "A 53-year-old man presents with a firm, painless mass in his left thigh noticed several weeks ago. Physical examination reveals a 6-cm subfascial lesion not attached to the overlying skin. A biopsy confirms a high-grade soft tissue sarcoma. Laboratory results show normal complete blood count, electrolytes, and lactate dehydrogenase. There is no evidence of enlarged lymph nodes on examination. Local imaging and surgical consultation are pending (see report).\nMRI of the thigh: Suspicious infiltrative mass\nWhich of the following imaging studies is the most appropriate next step in staging the most common site of metastasis for this tumor?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Bone scan of the axial skeleton"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Contrast-enhanced CT scan of the chest"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "MRI of the chest and mediastinum"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "text": "Whole-body PET scan"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 2,
      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=JN0sXg&anker=Z703218f8a38129d66a94750cc9880c97\" data-learningcard-id=\"JN0sXg\" data-anker=\"Z703218f8a38129d66a94750cc9880c97\" data-sememe-id=\"1Wb24s\">Bone scans</a> detect <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ho0KWS&anker=Z26c0518a6508198645f16e61d5388ed7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ho0KWS\" data-anker=\"Z26c0518a6508198645f16e61d5388ed7\" data-section-id=\"IocYWW0\" data-sememe-id=\"AJYR9J\">osteoblastic</a> activity and are used for cancers with a high propensity for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=oD002R&anker=Z3134d031d665d445006833ed1577753b\" data-learningcard-id=\"oD002R\" data-anker=\"Z3134d031d665d445006833ed1577753b\" data-sememe-id=\"d7aokN\">bone metastasis</a>, such as <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=l60vOS&anker=Z6193c696f64ae504f5c057459595b7f3\" data-learningcard-id=\"l60vOS\" data-anker=\"Z6193c696f64ae504f5c057459595b7f3\" data-section-id=\"jwc_ie0\" data-sememe-id=\"0rXefz\">prostate</a> or <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_k05qT&anker=Z3186a2e5e91124c9021effe4344433c7\" data-learningcard-id=\"_k05qT\" data-anker=\"Z3186a2e5e91124c9021effe4344433c7\" data-sememe-id=\"4M03Kg\">breast cancer</a>. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3E0Sv3&anker=Z7975f61036d6b5eeb3ec7d0f121aa02c\" data-learningcard-id=\"3E0Sv3\" data-anker=\"Z7975f61036d6b5eeb3ec7d0f121aa02c\" data-sememe-id=\"BPVzSu0\">Soft tissue sarcomas</a> typically <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=WM0Png&anker=Z56ce78424b29da57669d773285a33fa6\" data-learningcard-id=\"WM0Png\" data-anker=\"Z56ce78424b29da57669d773285a33fa6\" data-section-id=\"XzX9r00\" data-sememe-id=\"IrXYiz\">metastasize</a> to the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ap0QLS&anker=Z5a964768554f93e7967999032fda236f\" data-learningcard-id=\"ap0QLS\" data-anker=\"Z5a964768554f93e7967999032fda236f\">lungs</a>, not the skeleton, and there is no clinical indication of bone involvement in this patient.</div><div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) CORRECT:</h4>High-grade <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3E0Sv3&anker=Z7975f61036d6b5eeb3ec7d0f121aa02c\" data-learningcard-id=\"3E0Sv3\" data-anker=\"Z7975f61036d6b5eeb3ec7d0f121aa02c\" data-sememe-id=\"BPVzSu0\">soft tissue sarcomas</a> primarily <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=WM0Png&anker=Z56ce78424b29da57669d773285a33fa6\" data-learningcard-id=\"WM0Png\" data-anker=\"Z56ce78424b29da57669d773285a33fa6\" data-section-id=\"XzX9r00\" data-sememe-id=\"IrXYiz\">metastasize</a> to the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ap0QLS&anker=Z5a964768554f93e7967999032fda236f\" data-learningcard-id=\"ap0QLS\" data-anker=\"Z5a964768554f93e7967999032fda236f\">lungs</a> via hematogenous spread. A <span data-sememe-id=\"m1bVhs\">contrast-enhanced CT scan</span> of the chest is the preferred imaging modality for detecting <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=nh07ef&anker=Z10e1e58497265a96d804a98d36fd497b\" data-learningcard-id=\"nh07ef\" data-anker=\"Z10e1e58497265a96d804a98d36fd497b\" data-section-id=\"82aOjP\">pulmonary metastases</a> due to its high resolution and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ps0LDh&anker=Z252fcd07b99eb21a8bff067bee67fd9d\" data-learningcard-id=\"ps0LDh\" data-anker=\"Z252fcd07b99eb21a8bff067bee67fd9d\" data-section-id=\"EfW8Lk0\" data-sememe-id=\"wkXhJy\">sensitivity</a> for small <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_405NT&anker=Ze562e7aa25e368f0be0c7066c00f0243\" data-learningcard-id=\"_405NT\" data-anker=\"Ze562e7aa25e368f0be0c7066c00f0243\" data-section-id=\"-EXDy-\" data-sememe-id=\"YdXnoC\">nodules</a>. Intravenous contrast enhances vascular structures and lesion margins, aiding in the identification of subtle <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=WM0Png&anker=Z56ce78424b29da57669d773285a33fa6\" data-learningcard-id=\"WM0Png\" data-anker=\"Z56ce78424b29da57669d773285a33fa6\" data-section-id=\"XzX9r00\" data-sememe-id=\"IrXYiz\">metastatic</a> deposits. This approach aligns with <span data-sememe-id=\"LZUwXba\">staging</span> guidelines for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3E0Sv3&anker=Z7975f61036d6b5eeb3ec7d0f121aa02c\" data-learningcard-id=\"3E0Sv3\" data-anker=\"Z7975f61036d6b5eeb3ec7d0f121aa02c\" data-sememe-id=\"BPVzSu0\">soft tissue sarcomas</a>, ensuring accurate assessment of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=WM0Png&anker=Z56ce78424b29da57669d773285a33fa6\" data-learningcard-id=\"WM0Png\" data-anker=\"Z56ce78424b29da57669d773285a33fa6\" data-section-id=\"XzX9r00\" data-sememe-id=\"IrXYiz\">metastatic</a> spread.<br><br><span class=\"wichtig\"><b>Key learning point: </b></span>For <span data-sememe-id=\"LZUwXba\">staging</span> high-grade <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=WM0Png&anker=Z48199b498b89ace4a6e36311825d4376\" data-learningcard-id=\"WM0Png\" data-anker=\"Z48199b498b89ace4a6e36311825d4376\" data-section-id=\"azXQr00\" data-sememe-id=\"uQXpBB\">sarcomas</a>, a chest <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=KN0UXg&anker=Ze2b9f34cdbf89aef620d4cba111183d1\" data-learningcard-id=\"KN0UXg\" data-anker=\"Ze2b9f34cdbf89aef620d4cba111183d1\" data-sememe-id=\"Fn0gEg\">CT scan</a> is essential to evaluate for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=nh07ef&anker=Z10e1e58497265a96d804a98d36fd497b\" data-learningcard-id=\"nh07ef\" data-anker=\"Z10e1e58497265a96d804a98d36fd497b\" data-section-id=\"82aOjP\">pulmonary metastases</a>, as the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ap0QLS&anker=Z5a964768554f93e7967999032fda236f\" data-learningcard-id=\"ap0QLS\" data-anker=\"Z5a964768554f93e7967999032fda236f\">lungs</a> are the most common site of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=WM0Png&anker=Z56ce78424b29da57669d773285a33fa6\" data-learningcard-id=\"WM0Png\" data-anker=\"Z56ce78424b29da57669d773285a33fa6\" data-section-id=\"XzX9r00\" data-sememe-id=\"IrXYiz\">metastasis</a> for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=WM0Png&anker=Z48199b498b89ace4a6e36311825d4376\" data-learningcard-id=\"WM0Png\" data-anker=\"Z48199b498b89ace4a6e36311825d4376\" data-section-id=\"azXQr00\" data-sememe-id=\"uQXpBB\">sarcomas</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=pN0LXg&anker=Zefb6206a3f821bf7e5942b654dc6f6cf\" data-learningcard-id=\"pN0LXg\" data-anker=\"Zefb6206a3f821bf7e5942b654dc6f6cf\" data-sememe-id=\"8n0OEg\">MRI</a> is not ideal for evaluating <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ap0QLS&anker=Zbc4e2cd5b038bc04fba483dc59b22270\" data-learningcard-id=\"ap0QLS\" data-anker=\"Zbc4e2cd5b038bc04fba483dc59b22270\" data-section-id=\"OvcIZe0\">pulmonary parenchyma</a> due to lower spatial resolution and susceptibility to motion artifacts, which limit its ability to detect small pulmonary <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_405NT&anker=Ze562e7aa25e368f0be0c7066c00f0243\" data-learningcard-id=\"_405NT\" data-anker=\"Ze562e7aa25e368f0be0c7066c00f0243\" data-section-id=\"-EXDy-\" data-sememe-id=\"YdXnoC\">nodules</a>. While <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=pN0LXg&anker=Zefb6206a3f821bf7e5942b654dc6f6cf\" data-learningcard-id=\"pN0LXg\" data-anker=\"Zefb6206a3f821bf7e5942b654dc6f6cf\" data-sememe-id=\"8n0OEg\">MRI</a> provides excellent <span data-sememe-id=\"T4c6ic0\">soft tissue</span> contrast, it is more suitable for local <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=WM0Png&anker=Z333a818dbf71a509f924e54006a41fb6\" data-learningcard-id=\"WM0Png\" data-anker=\"Z333a818dbf71a509f924e54006a41fb6\" data-section-id=\"azXQr00\">tumor</a> characterization rather than <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=nh07ef&anker=Z10e1e58497265a96d804a98d36fd497b\" data-learningcard-id=\"nh07ef\" data-anker=\"Z10e1e58497265a96d804a98d36fd497b\" data-section-id=\"82aOjP\">lung metastasis</a> <span data-sememe-id=\"LZUwXba\">staging</span>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) INCORRECT:</h4>While <span data-sememe-id=\"_Ma5rO\">PET scans</span> evaluate metabolic activity and can identify active <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=WM0Png&anker=Z333a818dbf71a509f924e54006a41fb6\" data-learningcard-id=\"WM0Png\" data-anker=\"Z333a818dbf71a509f924e54006a41fb6\" data-section-id=\"azXQr00\">tumor</a> sites, they have limited <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ps0LDh&anker=Z252fcd07b99eb21a8bff067bee67fd9d\" data-learningcard-id=\"ps0LDh\" data-anker=\"Z252fcd07b99eb21a8bff067bee67fd9d\" data-section-id=\"EfW8Lk0\" data-sememe-id=\"wkXhJy\">sensitivity</a> for small pulmonary <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_405NT&anker=Ze562e7aa25e368f0be0c7066c00f0243\" data-learningcard-id=\"_405NT\" data-anker=\"Ze562e7aa25e368f0be0c7066c00f0243\" data-section-id=\"-EXDy-\" data-sememe-id=\"YdXnoC\">nodules</a> compared to CT. The <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ap0QLS&anker=Z5a964768554f93e7967999032fda236f\" data-learningcard-id=\"ap0QLS\" data-anker=\"Z5a964768554f93e7967999032fda236f\">lung</a> is the most common site of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=WM0Png&anker=Z56ce78424b29da57669d773285a33fa6\" data-learningcard-id=\"WM0Png\" data-anker=\"Z56ce78424b29da57669d773285a33fa6\" data-section-id=\"XzX9r00\" data-sememe-id=\"IrXYiz\">metastasis</a> for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3E0Sv3&anker=Z7975f61036d6b5eeb3ec7d0f121aa02c\" data-learningcard-id=\"3E0Sv3\" data-anker=\"Z7975f61036d6b5eeb3ec7d0f121aa02c\" data-sememe-id=\"BPVzSu0\">soft tissue sarcomas</a>, and CT provides superior spatial resolution for detecting early <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=nh07ef&anker=Z10e1e58497265a96d804a98d36fd497b\" data-learningcard-id=\"nh07ef\" data-anker=\"Z10e1e58497265a96d804a98d36fd497b\" data-section-id=\"82aOjP\">lung metastases</a>.</div>",
